data.description: This four bedroom home has convenient access to River Ranch, shopping, restaurants, Comeaux High School and Lady of Lourdes Hospital. Spacious home with a large living room features a wood burning fireplace and a vaulted ceiling.  The kitchen is open to the dining area that features a bay window. There is an air conditioned enclosed sun-room that overlooks the fenced in backyard.
